snippet.title: Families Facing Cash Crunch for Marriages after Rs 500, Rs 1,000 Ban

localized.description:
Families across the country are facing severe cash crunch amid marriage ceremonies after Rs 500 and Rs 1000 currency notes have been banned by Modi government. No one is accepting Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes and peoples can only withdraw ten thousand rupees and exchange only four thousand rupees at banks.
